## Layering
Follow `03-node.mdc` for responsibilities and error handling; not repeated here.

## Generation order
1. Zod schema → `lib/validators/[resource].ts`
2. Repository helpers (if new queries)
3. Service
4. Route handler

## Must include
- Zod-parse all inputs; 400 with details on failure

## Do not add
- Middleware unless asked
- Logging (user adds it)
- JSDoc noise
- Tests unless asked
